just_use wiki.go

# label: EARLY
# role: supports feature — browser-based read-only wiki for repo docs + sidecars + source

Promoted SPIKE → EARLY 2026-04-15 (Steve: "definitely keeping it
around"). Serves the repo as a read-only wiki at `/gopher/wiki/...`.
Landing = README.md rendered. Tree browsing at `/gopher/wiki/tree/*`.
Markdown rendered via goldmark; everything else shown as
preformatted text.

Security: path resolved against repo root (cwd at server start),
rejects any path that escapes via `..`.

Expected to evolve: comments, search, anchored feedback. Promote
to WORKHORSE once stable.
